org.jasig.cas

Class DefaultMessageDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.DefaultMessageDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, MessageDescriptor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PasswordExpiringWarningMessageDescriptor

    public class DefaultMessageDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageDescriptor
    Simple parameterized message descriptor with a code that refers to a message bundle key and a default message string to use if no message code can be resolved.
    Since:
    4.0.0
